newsitem.title: SWITZERLAND: SOCCER-GRASSHOPPER ZURICH V AJAX AMSTERDAM TEAMS.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-GRASSHOPPER ZURICH V AJAX AMSTERDAM TEAMS.

text.p: Teams for Wednesday's European Cup Champions' League group A match between Grasshopper Zurich of Switzerland and Ajax Amsterdam of the Netherlands:

Grasshopper Zurich: 1-Pascal Zuberbuehler, 3-Pascal Thueler, 4-Mats Gren, 6-Murat Yakin, 7-Antonio Esposito, 9-Viorel Moldovan, 10-Massimo Lombardo, 13-Georgios Nemtsoudis, 14-Johann Vogel, 15-Nestor Subiat, 29-Boris Smiljanic.

Ajax Amsterdam: 1-Edwin Van der Sar, 2-John Veldman, 3-Frank de Boer, 6-Ronald De Boer, 7-Tijani Babangida, 9-Patrick Kluivert, 11-Marc Overmars, 14- Martijn Reuser, 18-Kiki Musampa, 19-Arnold Scholten, 32-Arno Splinter.
